data.text:
Delegate: TARUN AMALNERKAR

Affiliation: Universiti Tunku Abdul Rahman (UTAR)

Short Bio: Following are the details of the event for your reference:

The International Webinar World Sleep Day 2024

Venue: Virtual / Zoom / Online platform

Date: 16 and 17 March 2024 Two (2) days

Time: 10AM to 4PM (Time in Malaysia)

Target group: All UTARians and Community.

Fee: Free

Organizer: The Centre for Healthy Minds and Wellbeing under the Department of Student Affairs (DSA) at Universiti Tunku Abdul Rahman (UTAR) Sungai Long Campus.

Activity: Activity or Activities:

Experts, physicians, researchers in the area of sleep & related attributes and other respected dignitaries were the part of this webinar.

I feel privileged that I was a part of the organizing committee (as a chairperson) & speaker for a session on overview of sleep disorders among the elderly. Ms. Navamani A/P Nagappon was Vice-Chairperson of the said event, and Ms. Lim Zhi Qing and Ms. Yap Yong Yun (UTAR students), have extended their help as technical Managers.

For your reference here is the link of the webpage.

Reference:

Website: https://news.utar.edu.my/news/2024/Mar/29/04/03.html

Location: Cheras,

Date of Activity: 16 and 17 March 2024 Two (2) days
